OL,3,CMan jailed for three years for killing
OL,4,Cwife
OL,6,FA former BBC security guard who beat
OL,7,Fhis wife to death with a hammer was
OL,8,Ftoday handed a seven-year sentence.
OL,10,FGary Alexander Baird pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Fa charge of the manslaughter of his
OL,12,Fwife Susan Baird on the grounds of
OL,13,Fdiminished responsibility.
OL,15,FHis sentence included three years jail
OL,16,Fwith four years to be served on
OL,17,Flicence. Given the time the 65-year-
OL,18,Fold served while awaiting trial he is
OL,19,Fto be released later this year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
