OL,3,CMan jailed for three years for killing
OL,4,Cwife
OL,6,FThe 60-year-old mother-of-four died
OL,7,Ffrom catastrophic head injures in the
OL,8,Fcouple's Windermere Road home in the
OL,9,FFour Winds area of Belfast on the
OL,10,Fafternoon of Sunday August 16, 2020.
OL,12,FAs the couple's four children sat in
OL,13,Fthe public gallery, Baird showed no
OL,14,Femotion as Mr Justice McFarland said:
OL,15,F"This was a vicious and brutal attack
OL,16,Fagainst his wife of nearly 40 years,
OL,17,Fwith a hammer."
OL,19,FAlso present for today's hearing where
OL,20,FMrs Baird's siblings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
