OL,6,FJustice McFarland said he has read
OL,7,F"moving" victim impact statements made
OL,8,Fby Mrs Baird's children, brother and
OL,9,Fsister.
OL,11,FHe said: "Each statement in its own
OL,12,Fway spoke eloquently about the
OL,13,Fdevastation caused by the death, about
OL,14,Fthe loss suffered by the sister,
OL,15,Fbrother and children as individuals
OL,16,Fand also the loss suffered by members
OL,17,Fof the wider family.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
