OL,3,CMan jailed for three years for killing
OL,4,Cwife
OL,6,F"For everyone this has been a deeply
OL,7,Femotional experience, particularly for
OL,8,Fthe children knowing that their mother
OL,9,Fhas been killed in such a brutal way
OL,10,Fby their father."
OL,12,FMr Justice McFarland also referenced a
OL,13,Fstatement made by one of Mrs Baird's
OL,14,Fchildren, which said: "On the 16th of
OL,15,FAugust 2020, my Dad killed my Mum.
OL,17,F"This will never get any easier to say
OL,18,Ffrom me. I struggle to write it, never
OL,19,Fmind say it aloud and I still find it
OL,20,Fextremely hard to believe this is our
OL,21,Freality."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
