OL,4,Cwife
OL,6,FAt the time of her death, Mrs Baird
OL,7,Fworked as an administrator at
OL,8,FOrangefield Presbyterian Church.
OL,10,FOn the afternoon of her death, she had
OL,11,Fspend some time working from home
OL,12,Funtil around 2.30pm.
OL,14,FAt 4.51pm, Baird called 999 and during
OL,15,Fthe 11-minute phonecall, he admitted
OL,16,Fhe had killed his wife.
OL,18,FDuring the call, Baird said: "I've
OL,19,Fjust murdered my wife."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
