OL,3,CMan jailed for three years for killing
OL,4,Cwife
OL,6,FTen days before killing his wife,
OL,7,FBaird jumped in front of a bin lorry
OL,8,Fas it drove down Bedford Street in
OL,9,FBelfast which resulted in him being
OL,10,Fhospitalised.
OL,12,FThe court heard that whilst there had
OL,13,Fbeen problems within the Baird's
OL,14,Fmarriage, there was no history of
OL,15,Fdomestic violence and that Mrs Baird
OL,16,Fhas been concerned about the decline
OL,17,Fin her husband's mental health.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
