OL,3,CMan jailed for three years for killing
OL,4,Cwife
OL,6,FShe has also expressed fears about his
OL,7,Fmental state after he was released
OL,8,Ffrom hospital following the incident
OL,9,Finvolving the bin lorry.
OL,11,FThis, Mr McFarland said, could have
OL,12,Fbeen an accident but may well have
OL,13,Fbeen an act of self-harm or an attempt
OL,14,Fat suicide.
OL,16,FIt also emerged that prior to the
OL,17,Ffatal hammer attack, over 570 calls
OL,18,Fhad been made to Baird's GP's practice
OL,19,Fin a bid to seek help - none of which
OL,20,Fwere answered.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
