OL,3,CMan jailed for three years for killing
OL,4,Cwife
OL,6,FAs a result of further medical
OL,7,Freports, this plea was accepted by the
OL,8,FCrown with today's sentencing marking
OL,9,Fthe conclusion of the case.
OL,11,FSpeaking after the sentence was
OL,12,Fimposed, the couple's children issued
OL,13,Fa statement which said: "As the four
OL,14,Fchildren of Susan Baird, we welcome
OL,15,Fand accept the verdict of manslaughter
OL,16,Fwith diminished responsibility.
OL,18,F"Through our immense heartbreak, we
OL,19,Fhope to see improvements and better
OL,20,Ffunding in mental health services
OL,21,Facross Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
