OL,6,F"All family members wish to extend
OL,7,Ftheir heartfelt thanks to all who have
OL,8,Fshown kindness, and we ask for privacy
OL,9,Fas we continue in our grief."
OL,11,FAlso reacting to today's sentencing
OL,12,Fwas Detective Inspector Jennifer Rea
OL,13,Ffrom the PSNI who said: "The
OL,14,Finvestigation began with the defendant
OL,15,Freporting his actions to police.
OL,17,F"While proceedings have concluded with
OL,18,Ftoday's sentencing, I know that the
OL,19,Fcouple's children, wider family and
OL,20,Ffriends remain submerged in sorrow. My
OL,21,Fsincere thoughts are with them."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/14
